thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by George & Stephaniee

author: George & Stephaniee
title: George & Stephaniee
text:
Hello,
We had Georgina Venetakis managing our property on Reservoir. From the begginning of our property managent , she went above and beyond to make sure she found the perfect tenants for our house. As this was our first investment property we didn't really understand how everything worked so Georgina took all the responsibility upon herself and we never once doubted her choices. Every time we had a question she promptly came up with a solution and made this process very easy for us. Would recommend to anyone!
